Rewrite the below JAVA program in Python and add a condition to print "Blast Off!" after the countdown is complete. Additionally, add a constraint that the program should not use any loops or recursion to achieve the countdown. Ensure that the time complexity of the solution is O(1).

#Original JAVA Code#
```java
public class Countdown {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int count = 10;
        while (count >= 0) {
            System.out.println(count);
            count--;
        }
        System.out.println("Blast Off!");
    }
}
```

#Rewritten Python Code#
```python
def countdown(count):
    if count >= 0:
        print(count)
        countdown(count - 1)
    else:
        print("Blast Off!")

countdown(10)
```

#Additional Constraints#
The rewritten Python code should not use any loops or recursion to achieve the countdown. The time complexity of the solution should be O(1).

